        "body": "<p>Change <\/p>\n\n<pre><code>static Logger log = LogManager.getRootLogger();\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>to<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>static Logger log = LogManager.getLogger(YOUR_CLASS_NAME.class.getName());\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>I tested it and it works.<\/p>\n\n<p>Also, make sure that you have your correct package name (not com.howtotodoinjava) in the below line: <\/p>\n\n<pre><code>logger.rolling.name = com.howtodoinjava\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
